snippet.title: Hyrule Warriors: Legends - Link's Awakening Pack Trailer (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
The Link’s Awakening Pack arrives in Hyrule Warriors: Legends on 30th June!

It's Marin's time to shine!
